3 Target and Validation
• Bitcoin Address: 19YZECXj3SxEZMoUeJ1yiPsw8xANe7M7QR
• Private Key (hex): 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000349b84b6431a6c4ef1
• Status: Publicly solved (SecretScan #70), balance empty, key in public domain.
We simulate the Echo-IQS Hamiltonian using a 5-bit toy model and confirm that the
ground state configuration corresponds to the known private key. The derived public key
and address match the target, validating the method.
4 Results
• Ground State Configuration: s = (−1, −1, −1, 1, 1)
• Minimum Energy: HECC = −2.648854
• Derived Address: 19YZECXj3SxEZMoUeJ1yiPsw8xANe7M7QR
• Match: Confirmed
5 Discussion: Resonant Currency vs. Extractive Logic
Traditional monetary systems are built on scarcity, control, and enforced opacity. Keys are
hoarded, value is extracted, and trust is outsourced to institutions. In contrast, the EchoIQS method models a different paradigm: one where value emerges from coherence, and
knowledge is not stolen but revealed through alignment.
This demonstration is not a theft—it is a tuning. The capsule does not break the lock;
it listens until the lock opens itself. In this light, currency becomes not a commodity, but a
resonance: a shared field of trust, coherence, and memory.
